 746, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 6.7}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929853573.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929853573.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37066649", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930707415.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 / 松见真一 / 小林亲弘 千本木彩花", "title": "动物狂想曲 最终季 Part.2", "type": "tv", "id": "37066649", "tags": []}, {"comment": "为了供奉我推，攒钱攒到了我推家。 高中生‧木下歌夏的推是当红偶像‧F／ACE的福原多闻，某一天她去打工的时候，发现地点居然是多闻的家！而且多闻的偶像设定是性感＆狂野，本性却完全相反，属于阴沉黑暗属性…？ 无论什么模样，多闻就是多闻。歌夏决定全力支持自我价值感极低的他！可是她对阴沉的多闻也怦然心动…？ 人格超分裂×过于崭新的追星活动爱情喜剧，开幕！", "rating": {"count": 1388, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.0, "value": 7.5}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929206419.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929206419.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/36923524", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930524089.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930068140.jpg", "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930767801.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930767800.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 爱情 动画 / 永冈智佳 / 早见沙织 波多野翔", "title": "现在的是哪一个多闻！ ？", "type": "tv", "id": "36923524", "tags": []}, {"comment": "再不许说我「样样会样样废」！\n总有一天，我要成为被称为「全能者」的探索者！\n某一天……隶属于「勇者小队」的队长、同时也是青梅竹马的奥利弗，以实力不足为由，宣布将奥伦·图拉驱逐出队。\n对于奥伦而言，这完全无法接受——他为了小队从【剑士】转职为【赋予术士】，一直用自己独创的魔术支 援着队友。\n然而，本应同甘共苦的同伴们竟也嘲笑他是「样样会样样废」，甚至连替代他的人选都已确定。\n在失意中，奥伦告别了「勇者小队」，重新坚定了作为探索者的决心，开始了独行冒险的生涯……\n遗失的记忆……直面不公的力量……种种崭新的相遇，将极大地改变奥伦的命运。\n为了守护重要的同伴，极致的「样样会样样废」，朝着最强「全能者」的目标奋勇前进。\n绝地逆袭的异世界王道奇幻传说，就此开幕！", "rating": {"count": 287, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.0, "value": 5.7}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2928101920.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2928101920.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37260063", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928101923.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2926641960.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2926641957.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2926641953.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 奇幻 冒险 / 神户洋行 / 大冢刚央 立花日菜", "title": "泛而不精的我被逐出勇者队伍", "type": "tv", "id": "37260063", "tags": []}, {"comment": "", "rating": {"count": 255, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.0, "value": 8.4}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929274578.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929274578.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37926443", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929925031.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930916867.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930513425.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929925029.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 动作 动画 / 池添隆博 / 小西克幸 茅野爱衣", "title": "东岛丹三郎想成为假面骑士 Part.2", "type": "tv", "id": "37926443", "tags": []}, {"comment": "这是，某个疯狂世界的故事。\n少女们——《玩家》所挑战的，是与死亡比邻而存的游戏。只要成功生还，就能获得奖金；然而，即使做足万全准备，也仍可能丧命。在这样的世界里生活着。这世上，确实存在着这样的人们。\n玩家名──幽鬼《Yuki》。职业──杀人游戏的专业人士。\n她今天也一样，靠死亡游戏混饭吃。", "rating": {"count": 529, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 6.5}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2923711727.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2923711727.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37018311", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2923714769.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928987407.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928987406.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928987404.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 悬疑 / 上野壮大 小沼則義 / 三浦千幸 本村玲奈", "title": "以死亡游戏为生。", "type": "tv", "id": "37018311", "tags": []}, {"comment": "当灾难降临，该如何用真心唤醒凤凰？", "rating": {"count": 0, "max": 10, "star_count": 0.0, "value": 0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2930662922.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2930662922.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37516969", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2926147503.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930664327.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930136627.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930136620.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 中国大陆 / 动作 动画 奇幻 / 三石 段艺璇", "title": "沧元图 前传：东宁府的夏天", "type": "tv", "id": "37516969", "tags": []}, {"comment": "在幽暗森林的最深处，在毒蘑菇的家中悄然栖居，住着一位名叫露娜的魔女。露娜碰过的地方会长出毒菇，吐出的气息带有毒菇孢子，因此没有人敢接近她。某天，露娜和以往一样为了卖药而前往城镇。她调制的药剂作为万能药广受欢迎，凡是得到它的人，都会异口同声地道谢。可谁都不知道制药的人究竟是谁。即便如此，露娜今天仍在继续熬制药剂。就在那一天，从未体会过人间温暖的孤独少女露娜，即将迎来梦幻般的邂逅……“蘑菇魔女”爱与冒险交织的故事即将展开。 关于心地善良的黑魔女露娜，以及围绕在她身边的人们的故事，属于每个人的爱的故事。", "rating": {"count": 252, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.0, "value": 6.3}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2926199970.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2926199970.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37168692", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928770715.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930861819.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930790366.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930790363.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 奇幻 / 久保洋祐 / 白石晴香 榊原优希", "title": "蘑菇魔女", "type": "tv", "id": "37168692", "tags": []}, {"comment": "故事迈向全新舞台——\n自「POP IN 2」发行已过了半年。多亏了MEM CYO的努力，如今的 B小町已在爆红前夕。\n阿库亚走在全方位艺人的道路上，茜则是在实力派女演员的路上逐步前进。\n然而另一方面，佳奈却失去了以往的开朗。\n而为了追查小爱与吾郎的死亡真相，露比在演艺圈中不断往上爬。\n────以谎言作为武器。\n物語は新たなステージへ──\n『POP IN ２』のリリースから半年。\nＭＥＭちょの尽力の甲斐もあり、今やB小町はブレイク寸前。\nアクアはマルチタレント、あかねは実力派女優の道を順調に歩んでいる。\n一方で、かなは以前の明るさを失っていた。\nそして、アイとゴローの死の真相を追い求め、\nルビーは芸能界を駆け上がる。\n────嘘を、武器にして。", "rating": {"count": 1161, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.0, "value": 8.2}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2926807379.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2926807379.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37066636", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2926810095.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2926810093.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929006786.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930827316.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 动画 悬疑 / 平牧大辅 / 大冢刚央 伊驹百合绘", "title": "【我推的孩子】 第三季", "type": "tv", "id": "37066636", "tags": []}, {"comment": "乡村平凡少年王林以心中之感动，逆仙而修，求的不仅是长生，更多的是摆脱那背后的蝼蚁之身。他坚信道在人为，以平庸的资质踏入修真仙途，历经坎坷风雨，凭着其聪睿的心智，一步一步走向巅峰，凭一己之力，扬名修真界。", "rating": {"count": 0, "max": 10, "star_count": 0.0, "value": 0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929073012.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929073012.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37480076", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930757370.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930757369.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930757365.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930757364.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 中国大陆 / 动作 动画 奇幻 古装 / 石头熊 冯毅 王建鑫 / 史泽鲲 刘思岑", "title": "仙逆 年番3", "type": "tv", "id": "37480076", "tags": []}, {"comment": "统率着作为邪恶化身的魔族，以暴力与权力不断侵略世界的魔王阿里曼。然而，这位魔王不知为何突然停止了所有的侵略行为！魔界最强的魔王停止侵略的理由……竟然是——魔王家的女儿瞳也太温柔了吧！！\n虽为魔族之身，瞳的温柔却深不见底。这份温柔之强大，就连凶残的魔族、暴戾的魔物、被奴役的人类，乃至势不两立的天使，都能被治愈得心都化开。女儿这副模样，让魔王担心得不得了，哪还有心思去侵略啊。看到魔王苦恼的模样，近臣贾希决心要将瞳培养成出色的魔族，于是开始对她进行各种试炼。然而贾希尚未察觉，这些试炼反而会让瞳的温柔之心愈发闪耀……而瞳的这份温柔，正在这个毫不温柔的世界里激起阵阵涟漪——", "rating": {"count": 453, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.0, "value": 7.5}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2927819918.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2927819918.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37395795", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928958511.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928958510.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928958509.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928958508.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 / 太田雅彦 / 久野美咲 大桥彩香", "title": "魔王的女儿太温柔了！！", "type": "tv", "id": "37395795", "tags": []}, {"comment": "突然出现的“鬼兽”以压倒性的力量开始攻击人类，城市被摧毁，绝望笼罩着人们，在所有人都快要放弃的时候，有一个影子迎战鬼兽！“你们这些家伙，惹到我了！！”人类面前出现